arm_group.description:
Schools that are randomized to this arm will be exposed to the following components of the intervention:
Availability of the fully functional online CyberRwanda web portal through school-based cyber clubs;
SMS-based ordering of contraceptives and SMS-based FAQs Online (through web portal on computer or smartphone) ordering of contraceptives;
Facility finder: A list of the closest health centers and pharmacies where youth can get contraceptives and other FPRH services;
Promotion of the CyberRwanda program through school launch events; and
Access to Youth Centers (1 per district) that will house tablets with the fully functional online CyberRwanda web portal

criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Attending a study school at baseline;

          -  Between 12 and 19 years of age;

          -  Assent to participate;

          -  Parents have provided consent for their child to participate in the study; and

          -  Willingness to provide valid contact information for study follow-up purposes.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        -
